00:00:00.120 --> 00:00:53.289
I’m very happy to

00:00:53.289 --> 00:00:58.539
be here with you, after such a long time and
I missed you all very much.

00:00:58.539 --> 00:01:05.580
I know you are very far away from the rest
of them but you are always in My heart and

00:01:05.580 --> 00:01:11.530
you shouldn’t worry about the distance.

00:01:11.530 --> 00:01:16.520
We have to realize that we have entered into
a new, a….

00:01:16.520 --> 00:01:24.250
This kind of hands you should [HAVE, HAND],
not to hang, if you have to sit properly.

00:01:24.250 --> 00:01:31.890
You have to understand that we have now entered
into the Kingdom of God and our culture has

00:01:31.890 --> 00:01:39.020
to change, our style has to change, our understanding
has to change.

00:01:39.020 --> 00:01:43.660
Unless until we change, nobody’s going to
take us seriously.

00:01:43.660 --> 00:01:50.400
Moreover it’s very difficult to trigger
things if there’s no perfect instrument.

00:01:50.400 --> 00:01:56.960
As you know that I went to Russia second time
for the Yoga seminar, where we had people

00:01:56.960 --> 00:02:00.730
from all over the Eastern Block.

00:02:00.730 --> 00:02:03.660
That was My idea, to get them there.

00:02:03.660 --> 00:02:09.969
And they were from every country, about two
or three people, only.

00:02:09.969 --> 00:02:14.390
And very strong, very deep, very understanding.

00:02:14.390 --> 00:02:23.430
I spoke hardly for 30 minutes and such a miracle,
in fifteen minutes I gave them Realization,

00:02:23.430 --> 00:02:34.310
about ten minutes and five minutes I was just
there, and all of them got practically Realization,

00:02:34.310 --> 00:02:35.310
all of them.

00:02:35.310 --> 00:02:36.310
Very surprising.

00:02:36.310 --> 00:02:39.459
And so deeply, when I walked out of the room,
they all came after Me.

00:02:39.459 --> 00:02:43.510
That you don’t see in western countries,
that kind of a thing.

00:02:43.510 --> 00:02:47.810
All of them walked after Me, ran after Me,
they wanted to give their addresses and they

00:02:47.810 --> 00:02:51.230
wanted Me to go to their country and this
and that.

00:02:51.230 --> 00:02:53.859
I said: “All right, I’ll come!”

00:02:53.859 --> 00:02:57.060
We took their addresses, even from Romania,
everywhere.

00:02:57.060 --> 00:03:00.620
And they went back.

00:03:00.620 --> 00:03:04.819
And within 8 days one could trigger out the
thing.

00:03:04.819 --> 00:03:19.069
It worked, because they were so deep, because
they were so much equipped to trigger the

00:03:19.069 --> 00:03:20.069
happening.

00:03:20.069 --> 00:03:24.129
That’s how they triggered their country
and how they worked it out.

00:03:24.129 --> 00:03:31.760
So, if we live on a superficial level of Sahaja
Yoga, then we cannot do much for ourselves

00:03:31.760 --> 00:03:37.749
nor for the country and it’s just a wasteful
life, neither here nor there.

00:03:37.749 --> 00:03:41.999
Is like a seed, which is sprouted and has
not grown into the tree.

00:03:41.999 --> 00:03:47.930
So first of all we have to learn that we have
to become very deep people, very deep, you

00:03:47.930 --> 00:03:49.610
must teach our depth.

00:03:49.610 --> 00:03:55.260
I’ve heard that people come to Pujas and
things and their main interest is in food.

00:03:55.260 --> 00:03:58.959
As soon as the Puja is over you just rush
for food.

00:03:58.959 --> 00:04:01.349
How can you?

00:04:01.349 --> 00:04:06.969
After Puja you get into a mood, after meditation
you get into a mood of meditating nature and

00:04:06.969 --> 00:04:11.420
you just sit down and you can’t get up,
because you were fallen into the well and

00:04:11.420 --> 00:04:12.540
sort of thing happens.

00:04:12.540 --> 00:04:16.139
How can you just get up and walk for cakes
or things.

00:04:16.139 --> 00:04:18.319
We though can’t think about.

00:04:18.319 --> 00:04:22.300
So then judge yourself, how you are, how far
you are.

00:04:22.300 --> 00:04:33.280
You have to work out your vibrations because
you are going to create that beautiful vision

00:04:33.280 --> 00:04:38.759
in this country, for your children, for yourself
and for the whole country, ultimately for

00:04:38.759 --> 00:04:41.700
the whole world.

00:04:41.700 --> 00:04:45.699
But if you do not take it up seriously, just
by the way, Sahaja Yoga is just by the way,

00:04:45.699 --> 00:04:47.180
it doesn’t work out.

00:04:47.180 --> 00:04:49.680
It has to be way of life.

00:04:49.680 --> 00:04:53.250
And in everything that you do it has to be
a Sahaj culture.

00:04:53.250 --> 00:04:59.539
And in Sahaj culture so many things are to
be understood that this is natural, this is

00:04:59.539 --> 00:05:03.400
real and we have to accept the way it is.

00:05:03.400 --> 00:05:08.570
So many things are happening the West, which
I think are just destructive, absolutely destructive

00:05:08.570 --> 00:05:09.960
to the society.

00:05:09.960 --> 00:05:14.590
The society is not at all looked after, here.

00:05:14.590 --> 00:05:23.150
Maybe I would blame this to the women of Australia
and New Zealand, that women are not understanding

00:05:23.150 --> 00:05:32.690
their responsibility and do not understand
what is their [GLORY], also they have not

00:05:32.690 --> 00:05:33.840
self esteem.

00:05:33.840 --> 00:05:37.830
The other day I was traveling by plane and
most of the ladies were smoking and men were

00:05:37.830 --> 00:05:39.280
not smoking.

00:05:39.280 --> 00:05:43.210
Men were looking after the children, the women
were busy smoking like men, you see, looking

00:05:43.210 --> 00:05:45.020
like half men half women.

00:05:45.020 --> 00:05:48.919
It’s surprising, this is very destructive.

00:05:48.919 --> 00:05:54.229
Because as I have said that that men and women
are like two wheels of a chariot, one on the

00:05:54.229 --> 00:05:55.600
left, one on the right.

00:05:55.600 --> 00:05:59.409
The left cannot go to the right and right
cannot go to the left.

00:05:59.409 --> 00:06:05.400
So we have to understand that our role is
much more important than of the other.

00:06:05.400 --> 00:06:11.189
Like the men have an important role, as well
as the women have even more important role.

00:06:11.189 --> 00:06:13.630
To be a mother itself is a very big thing.

00:06:13.630 --> 00:06:16.520
Why God has given you the motherhood?

00:06:16.520 --> 00:06:22.310
Because God thinks you are like the Mother
Earth, that you look after, nourish the child,

00:06:22.310 --> 00:06:25.009
nourish the family, do all these things.

00:06:25.009 --> 00:06:32.860
Don’t try to follow the methods of men,
like smoking, drinking, behaving like them.

00:06:32.860 --> 00:06:37.100
You just see the trend, how far it is going,
the self-esteem is so low.

00:06:37.100 --> 00:06:43.680
Now, for women, the other day I was, I was
telling you about the way they are talking

00:06:43.680 --> 00:06:46.970
about sexy, sexy women.

00:06:46.970 --> 00:06:52.240
I mean it’s…one should be ashamed of saying
such a thing for women.

00:06:52.240 --> 00:06:55.860
Because one should take an objection: “We
are not prostitutes that every man should

00:06:55.860 --> 00:06:57.789
look at us and enjoy us.

00:06:57.789 --> 00:06:58.789
Why?

00:06:58.789 --> 00:07:04.250
Are we sold out for them or are we something
for show?”

00:07:04.250 --> 00:07:08.810
The women have no self-esteem, they fight
on wrong things, they don’t fight on the

00:07:08.810 --> 00:07:09.810
right things.

00:07:09.810 --> 00:07:14.250
The right is that you should be respected
and you should not be treated like something

00:07:14.250 --> 00:07:19.990
on the show, that any man can look at you
and any, that the men should look at you,

00:07:19.990 --> 00:07:21.280
then you have some value.

00:07:21.280 --> 00:07:22.280
It’s nonsense.

00:07:22.280 --> 00:07:29.400
This is not the way to make great nations
and great children and great families.

00:07:29.400 --> 00:07:37.039
So the society of any country depends on the
women, which is a very solid work, which is

00:07:37.039 --> 00:07:39.800
underground, they don’t want to show off.

00:07:39.800 --> 00:07:44.449
Any country, which has got good women make
good society.

00:07:44.449 --> 00:07:47.629
And I must say the credit goes to Indian women,
in India.

00:07:47.629 --> 00:07:51.469
They have not bothered about these things,
you see, they are not bothered about their

00:07:51.469 --> 00:07:52.990
looks and the sexy nonsense.

00:07:52.990 --> 00:07:57.860
If somebody says them: “too sexy” I mean
they will slap you, feel very hurt: “What

00:07:57.860 --> 00:08:00.389
is this, what do you think us to be?”

00:08:00.389 --> 00:08:04.389
And to be proud of what work you are doing,
of course you have to work outside and do

00:08:04.389 --> 00:08:08.539
something else, but who will look after the
children, who will manage the households,

00:08:08.539 --> 00:08:11.370
who will keep the peace of the house is to
be seen.

00:08:11.370 --> 00:08:16.099
So in Sahaj culture one must understand that
women have to be women and men have to be

00:08:16.099 --> 00:08:17.099
men.

00:08:17.099 --> 00:08:20.080
But men must learn to respect the women as
housewives.

00:08:20.080 --> 00:08:22.979
[THE AUSTRALIAN DOES] respect them very much.

00:08:22.979 --> 00:08:29.039
If they do not respect their women then also
they will retaliate, they will get rebellier

00:08:29.039 --> 00:08:31.990
and there is all this women’s [REBELLION]
that has started.

00:08:31.990 --> 00:08:36.070
Is the mistake of men not the women so much,
because they have challenge their personality

00:08:36.070 --> 00:08:39.510
so much that now they have started behaving
like this.

00:08:39.510 --> 00:08:44.770
So in Sahaja Yoga we respect the women, we
allow them their own freedom, we trust them

00:08:44.770 --> 00:08:46.029
and we treat them equal.

00:08:46.029 --> 00:08:47.170
They have to be equal.

00:08:47.170 --> 00:08:50.050
They may not be similar but they are equal.

00:08:50.050 --> 00:08:55.440
The both the wheels have to be equal otherwise
wheel, one is smaller, one is bigger, then

00:08:55.440 --> 00:08:59.010
the chariot will never move forward, it will
go round and round and round.

00:08:59.010 --> 00:09:04.471
So that is to be understood, that’s very
much important nowadays in the West because

00:09:04.471 --> 00:09:09.260
I find slowly the derailment is towards hell.

00:09:09.260 --> 00:09:15.350
All these thoughts are going to take people
to nowhere because nobody takes the responsibility

00:09:15.350 --> 00:09:20.490
of molding a moral, creating moral values
for children.

00:09:20.490 --> 00:09:23.209
You have to give proper breeding.

00:09:23.209 --> 00:09:26.339
These days I find children are very undisciplined
here.

00:09:26.339 --> 00:09:28.639
Because we are afraid to face them.

00:09:28.639 --> 00:09:32.750
You have to face them and you have to tell
them that: “This is not so, you are Sahaja

00:09:32.750 --> 00:09:34.880
Yogis and you have to behave like Sahaja Yogis.”

00:09:34.880 --> 00:09:37.620
They have to be modest, they have to be humble.

00:09:37.620 --> 00:09:41.320
There should be a kind of an awe for parents.

00:09:41.320 --> 00:09:46.010
If they don’t have that awe for their parents
how can they have awe for Me or for God?

00:09:46.010 --> 00:09:47.010
They cannot.

00:09:47.010 --> 00:09:48.720
Whatever you may tell them they will not have.

00:09:48.720 --> 00:09:54.730
If they have no awe at all for the parents
who are Sahaja Yogis that means these children

00:09:54.730 --> 00:09:59.860
will become very ward like other children
and that is a very big risk you are running

00:09:59.860 --> 00:10:04.040
because I am depending on the children who
are born Realized and I don’t want them

00:10:04.040 --> 00:10:09.779
to go haywire because the parents have not
looked after them and faced them.

00:10:09.779 --> 00:10:14.690
So on the whole we must understand the role
of men and women and the respect that you

00:10:14.690 --> 00:10:16.100
have to pay to each other.

00:10:16.100 --> 00:10:20.710
Now, if husband is not respectful to woman
then the children will not be respectful to

00:10:20.710 --> 00:10:27.600
her and the whole thing will be finished and
that’s why there is no domination of anyone

00:10:27.600 --> 00:10:33.600
as such, there should not be any domination
but everybody has one’s own role and where

00:10:33.600 --> 00:10:37.420
the wife is concerned she should take a decision,
where the man is concerned, he should take

00:10:37.420 --> 00:10:42.060
a decision and one must respect it because
these are two different areas in which the

00:10:42.060 --> 00:10:44.720
man has to live and the woman has to live.

00:10:44.720 --> 00:10:49.750
Wherever this balance goes out, it has gone
out in our country also we should say, in

00:10:49.750 --> 00:10:53.720
India, I must say, there are now funny things
are happening thanks to the Muslims, who lived

00:10:53.720 --> 00:10:59.320
there and had such an impact that we are having
dowry system and all kinds of other things

00:10:59.320 --> 00:11:00.900
there we have.

00:11:00.900 --> 00:11:04.860
But also there are societies, which are trying
to work it out, they are not Sahaja Yogis

00:11:04.860 --> 00:11:09.920
but work it out, they are getting improved
and they are trying to change their ways and

00:11:09.920 --> 00:11:14.829
methods and this is coming before the people
to see that things should be all right.

00:11:14.829 --> 00:11:18.579
But supposing the women would have taken some
sort of a weapon in their hands and started

00:11:18.579 --> 00:11:20.570
beating all the men what would have happened?

00:11:20.570 --> 00:11:23.440
You see, you are complementary to each other.

00:11:23.440 --> 00:11:28.610
So must understand first of all, our role
in Sahaja Yoga that we have to establish our

00:11:28.610 --> 00:11:33.240
self-esteem and we have to respect ourselves
and we have to respect others.

00:11:33.240 --> 00:11:41.680
Because you are all saints and saints have
to respect people…

00:11:41.680 --> 00:11:47.079
I’ve been talking all the time.

00:11:47.079 --> 00:11:53.459
So you have to respect the saints that you
are a saint and another one is a saint.

00:11:53.459 --> 00:11:55.139
I always give the example of Namadeva.

00:11:55.139 --> 00:12:01.800
Namadeva was a tailor, the great poet and
a great saint.

00:12:01.800 --> 00:12:09.519
And he went to see another one who’s name
was Gora Khumbar who was a potter.

00:12:09.519 --> 00:12:15.449
And when he went to see him, Gora Khumbar
was busy knitting the clay to make the pots,

00:12:15.449 --> 00:12:19.430
see, just with his feet he was knitting the
clay.

00:12:19.430 --> 00:12:20.660
He looked at him.

00:12:20.660 --> 00:12:24.020
When he looked at him, he just stood thoughtless.

00:12:24.020 --> 00:12:31.300
And then the words he says so beautiful, he
said: “I have come to see the Nirakara,

00:12:31.300 --> 00:12:37.920
the Nirguna, the thought...the formless, means
the vibrations.

00:12:37.920 --> 00:12:43.620
I came to see the vibrations but here it is
in the form, standing”.

00:12:43.620 --> 00:12:52.050
What an appreciation, what an adoration, from
one saint to another who have never seen the

00:12:52.050 --> 00:12:53.050
other person.

00:12:53.050 --> 00:13:01.350
“But I see the whole of this Nirakara, the
Nirguna is in the form of you.”

00:13:01.350 --> 00:13:03.970
Just think of it.

00:13:03.970 --> 00:13:05.740
And that is what we have to be.

00:13:05.740 --> 00:13:11.089
But if we cannot trust other Sahaja Yogis,
we cannot love each other, we cannot understand

00:13:11.089 --> 00:13:14.850
each other that means we are something low,
lower than others.

00:13:14.850 --> 00:13:19.250
Some people have a habit of criticizing all
the time: “This is not all right”.

00:13:19.250 --> 00:13:22.779
They don’t see that there’s something
wrong with them within themselves that they

00:13:22.779 --> 00:13:24.150
are criticizing others.

00:13:24.150 --> 00:13:28.180
So there’s no chance for criticizing in
Sahaja Yoga, first thing is that you should

00:13:28.180 --> 00:13:33.430
see yourself what you are and where you stand
and how you are going to help yourself first

00:13:33.430 --> 00:13:34.430
of all.

00:13:34.430 --> 00:13:35.899
Then you can help others.

00:13:35.899 --> 00:13:42.230
But there is no need at all to put a critical
eye on others.

00:13:42.230 --> 00:13:46.170
Because then you become good for nothing,
you’ve done all the bad things, you see

00:13:46.170 --> 00:13:51.279
all the bad things in other people and what
do you develop is a non-collective personality,

00:13:51.279 --> 00:13:57.510
which is such a headache to us and ultimately
you have to go out of Sahaja Yoga.

00:13:57.510 --> 00:14:04.100
As I said there are two forces that are working
in Sahaja Yoga.

00:14:04.100 --> 00:14:20.779
The first one is the one by which you are
attracted, is called as, is called as the

00:14:20.779 --> 00:14:30.600
centripetal force, centripetal force by which
you are attracted and the another force is,

00:14:30.600 --> 00:14:34.209
is called as the centrifugal force.

00:14:34.209 --> 00:14:40.600
Supposing you have a stone attached to a string,
and you move it with a speed, you see, so

00:14:40.600 --> 00:14:46.250
you can keep it moving like that but as soon
as you release it a little bit it can go as

00:14:46.250 --> 00:14:47.870
a tangent.

00:14:47.870 --> 00:14:54.110
In the same way there are two forces by which
one we are attracted towards Sahaja Yoga,

00:14:54.110 --> 00:15:02.920
we keep one with it, we become part and parcel
of the whole, another one is by which we go

00:15:02.920 --> 00:15:03.920
out.

00:15:03.920 --> 00:15:07.790
Now I find that going out has become a very
strong force.

00:15:07.790 --> 00:15:14.470
And I get quite worried about it, not only
that you go out but you go out with very great

00:15:14.470 --> 00:15:15.470
problems.

00:15:15.470 --> 00:15:24.660
And this is what I’ve seen in
Australia very much working out.

00:15:24.660 --> 00:15:30.379
First of all if anybody says against Me or
Sahaja Yoga just close your eyes.

00:15:30.379 --> 00:15:35.639
Just say: “We don’t want to hear anything
against it because we have been benefited

00:15:35.639 --> 00:15:41.649
by, we got all the profits out of it and now
you don’t tell us anything.

00:15:41.649 --> 00:15:42.970
We don’t want to hear it.”

00:15:42.970 --> 00:15:48.410
Just close your eyes and cover your ears and
say: “We don’t want to hear it”.

00:15:48.410 --> 00:15:53.569
But we had three cases now where people are
suffering from cancer or this or that, who

00:15:53.569 --> 00:15:54.649
listened to this.

