The man who says may not get it, he may not,
but the one…because he’s already out,

00:16:00.620 --> 00:16:05.680
but the one who’s a Sahaja Yogi if he listens
to this thing is very dangerous and should

00:16:05.680 --> 00:16:11.140
not listen to anyone like that, who talks
ill about Me or about Sahaja Yoga.

00:16:11.140 --> 00:16:14.339
This is one point we should understand.

00:16:14.339 --> 00:16:19.899
And then those who find faults with other
Sahaja Yogis are also in trouble.

00:16:19.899 --> 00:16:21.860
You shouldn’t find faults with other Sahaja
Yogis.

00:16:21.860 --> 00:16:28.069
If you think there’s something wrong with
any Sahaja Yogi you can go and tell the leader.

00:16:28.069 --> 00:16:33.589
If you find anything wrong with the leader
you are welcome to write to Me, immediately.

00:16:33.589 --> 00:16:34.600
