Now I cannot keep attention on Columbia where
I’ve been, I cannot keep attention on America,

00:17:37.419 --> 00:17:40.150
but when I go there My attention is there.

00:17:40.150 --> 00:17:43.289
But if somebody has any problem they should
write to Me.

00:17:43.289 --> 00:17:50.409
Like this I’ve seen we have got lots of
problems and many Sahaja Yogis have left Sahaja

00:17:50.409 --> 00:17:51.640
Yoga.

00:17:51.640 --> 00:17:53.179
