to Me.

00:17:59.100 --> 00:18:03.670
But for small things they will write, somebody’s
wife is sick, or somebody’s father in law

00:18:03.670 --> 00:18:08.330
is in the hospital, or all nonsensical things,
like that they will write.

00:18:08.330 --> 00:18:12.880
But they will never tell Me that there’s
something is wrong with the leader, till I

00:18:12.880 --> 00:18:18.289
discover it, till the whole Sahaja Yoga is
destroyed in that particular city.

00:18:18.289 --> 00:18:23.669
So it’s my humble request that all of you
should know that I’m your Mother, directly.

00:18:23.669 --> 00:18:29.690
I’ve nothing to do with the leaders, as
far as you people are concerned.

00:18:29.690 --> 00:18:35.000
Any leader who is harsh on you, who’s troublesome
to you, who disciplines you too much, or tries

00:18:35.000 --> 00:18:40.860
to put his ideas all the time on your heads,
or anything like that which you think is curving

00:18:40.860 --> 00:18:44.860
your freedom of growth, you must write to
Me and you must know.

00:18:44.860 --> 00:18:50.330
This is no excuse to say that the leader was
like this, so [UNCLEAR] or “We went away.”

00:18:50.330 --> 00:18:51.330
Why did you go away?

00:18:51.330 --> 00:18:54.059
What was the need?

00:18:54.059 --> 00:19:00.770
And this I find very common, specially in
Australians and New Zealanders.

00:19:00.770 --> 00:19:11.070
Either they become just like complete slaves
or they become absolutely rebellious.

00:19:11.070 --> 00:19:13.480
There’s nothing in between.

00:19:13.480 --> 00:19:19.680
So you have to know that if there is anything
that you find which is trying to dominate

00:19:19.680 --> 00:19:24.870
you, you must let us know, and I am always
going to correct and tell them on their faces,

00:19:24.870 --> 00:19:27.610
all the leaders, what I think of them.

00:19:27.610 --> 00:19:32.940
Because they also know that I’m sitting
down there to look after this.

00:19:32.940 --> 00:19:36.890
Of course about leaders I’ve given them
so many times, so many lectures and things

00:19:36.890 --> 00:19:42.480
and every time they come to Ganapatipule we
try to meet and talk about it and if there

00:19:42.480 --> 00:19:45.460
is any problem you have to find it pointed
out.

00:19:45.460 --> 00:19:49.730
But here I don’t know but in Australia,
specially, the thing what happened, whatever

00:19:49.730 --> 00:19:55.510
the leaders were doing, the same thing penetrated
into many Sahaja Yogis and they became sort

00:19:55.510 --> 00:20:04.960
of half leaders and they used to sort of dominate
people and say things which are not at all

00:20:04.960 --> 00:20:05.960
Sahaj.

00:20:05.960 --> 00:20:12.370
Like last year was all right, before that
they started saying Australia is great, we

00:20:12.370 --> 00:20:18.110
are the greatest thing, this, that, then half
of the Sahaja Yogis have left them.

00:20:18.110 --> 00:20:23.260
Talking so big and bombastically, even the
Indians were surprised, they started looking

00:20:23.260 --> 00:20:25.610
at them thinking what’s gone wrong with
them.

00:20:25.610 --> 00:20:30.340
And they reported to Me that: “They would
not listen to anyone, we told them that: ’Please,

00:20:30.340 --> 00:20:33.039
better start, we have to go now’ they would
not listen.

00:20:33.039 --> 00:20:35.039
They said: ‘Our leader has to tell us.’.

00:20:35.039 --> 00:20:37.440
They said: “Mother has said”.

00:20:37.440 --> 00:20:39.370
“Mother, no, our leader.”

00:20:39.370 --> 00:20:44.860
So even the leaders had replaced Me completely
because of these few people who joined hands

00:20:44.860 --> 00:20:46.260
with the others like.

00:20:46.260 --> 00:20:50.340
We can say, like the bureaucracy of Russia.

00:20:50.340 --> 00:20:55.890
There is no bureaucracy, there is no priesthood
in Sahaja Yoga, everybody is equally the same.

00:20:55.890 --> 00:21:02.390
They’re all saints, are to be respected
and all the leaders must respect you and understand

00:21:02.390 --> 00:21:03.390
you.

00:21:03.390 --> 00:21:08.870
Of course if you have any problems on chakras
that must be told, that is their job and for

00:21:08.870 --> 00:21:10.559
that you should be thankful.

00:21:10.559 --> 00:21:14.909
Instead of feeling bad about it you should
be thankful to them that: “Yes, that is

00:21:14.909 --> 00:21:19.260
so and we‘ll try to correct ourselves.”

00:21:19.260 --> 00:21:24.570
Now the better part of it that now suddenly
I find there’s a big explosion of Sahaja

00:21:24.570 --> 00:21:29.980
Yoga going on in various places where are
least expected like [UNCLEAR] and we have

00:21:29.980 --> 00:21:33.049
other places like Turkey and Russia.

00:21:33.049 --> 00:21:35.419
It’s something so remarkable is happening.

00:21:35.419 --> 00:21:42.200
So Sahaja Yoga is taking its fruits well and
maybe these people might grow much faster

00:21:42.200 --> 00:21:45.230
so you have to be careful, you should not
be left behind.

00:21:45.230 --> 00:21:50.060
Because there is one thing I’ve given an
indication, I don’t know if you have told

00:21:50.060 --> 00:21:57.690
them, last, this Ganapatipule that there is
going to be another jump, another triggering.

00:21:57.690 --> 00:22:08.570
I always give the analogy of a air space,
you see, space craft, like we can say the

00:22:08.570 --> 00:22:16.820
Sputnik or something, the principle of that,
same is applied to our evolution.

00:22:16.820 --> 00:22:21.970
Like first is one container, which has three,
four containers in it.

00:22:21.970 --> 00:22:29.810
So the first container goes half way and then
an explosion takes place and then the rest

00:22:29.810 --> 00:22:31.309
of it is thrown out.

00:22:31.309 --> 00:22:37.640
So the first speed, that is the velocity that
it has, gets absolutely accelerated and goes

00:22:37.640 --> 00:22:39.730
with a much greater speed.

00:22:39.730 --> 00:22:44.309
Then the second one explodes and then the
same thing happens, that’s how the speed

00:22:44.309 --> 00:22:47.159
they ultimately they achieve is very high
up.

00:22:47.159 --> 00:22:55.360
In the same way I feel that in Sahaja Yoga
is now happening and is the time for you to

00:22:55.360 --> 00:22:57.160
know there is going to be another triggering.

00:22:57.160 --> 00:23:01.210
And that triggering you have to catch up with.

00:23:01.210 --> 00:23:07.490
For that you should be prepared, otherwise
you will be left in the container which is

00:23:07.490 --> 00:23:09.630
just not to be used to it.

00:23:09.630 --> 00:23:15.500
So a new triggering, a new jumping out has
to be done and for that you have to hurry

00:23:15.500 --> 00:23:17.950
up and there’s no time to be lost.

00:23:17.950 --> 00:23:24.470
So the most important thing is that we should
develop ourselves into that capacity that

00:23:24.470 --> 00:23:29.929
we can jump on to the new triggering that
is going to take place in Sahaja Yoga.

00:23:29.929 --> 00:23:34.529
So I have to warn you though you are few you
have to have a quality, quantity does not

00:23:34.529 --> 00:23:37.960
matter, because so much of quantity might
drop out.

00:23:37.960 --> 00:23:43.630
So the thing is those who really want to ascent
must understand that we must meditate morning,

00:23:43.630 --> 00:23:48.480
evening and we must be absolutely collective.

00:23:48.480 --> 00:23:53.850
If we are not collective then there’s something
serious with us, something wrong with us and

00:23:53.850 --> 00:23:55.500
we have to correct it.

00:23:55.500 --> 00:24:01.230
So these are the things I wanted to tell you
and I must say that the collective here will

00:24:01.230 --> 00:24:07.940
now grow very much because of what we did,
today’s miracle that has taken place.

00:24:07.940 --> 00:24:13.590
Yesterday we had lots of people, every time
I come there are at least three hundred people

00:24:13.590 --> 00:24:16.720
and I knew there will be this time also.

00:24:16.720 --> 00:24:25.770
But what is the difference, when I come they
are there and then they don’t come or even

00:24:25.770 --> 00:24:27.700
if they come they disappear.

00:24:27.700 --> 00:24:31.130
They must have confidence in you.

00:24:31.130 --> 00:24:35.659
First you must have confidence in yourself.

00:24:35.659 --> 00:24:38.750
You must approach them in a way that they
feel confident.

00:24:38.750 --> 00:24:43.559
They shouldn’t feel that: “Some silly
stupid people are sitting here just telling

00:24:43.559 --> 00:24:45.150
us about these things”.

00:24:45.150 --> 00:24:54.800
But you must have that dignity, you must have
that approach, you must have that understanding,

00:24:54.800 --> 00:24:59.600
then only it will work out, otherwise you
cannot work it out.

00:24:59.600 --> 00:25:09.760
My own idea is that wherever there are very
good deep Sahaja Yogis people stick on.

00:25:09.760 --> 00:25:12.309
Like Austria, I would say.

00:25:12.309 --> 00:25:19.230
In Austria we have quite a lot of [NEW] people
now, [MILAN] we have quite a lot of people.

00:25:19.230 --> 00:25:26.809
The reason is both the places, I’ve noticed,
the Sahaja Yogis are of a very great quality.

00:25:26.809 --> 00:25:29.429
They are all working it out.

00:25:29.429 --> 00:25:36.809
Like there’s one boy who has fished out
lots of things from Quran, in German, from

00:25:36.809 --> 00:25:39.480
Quran, what it has to say for Sahaj.

00:25:39.480 --> 00:25:46.799
And they said there is a Sura called Shasta
Yoga, Shasta Yoga and that Sura is dealing

00:25:46.799 --> 00:25:47.799
with Me.

00:25:47.799 --> 00:25:52.390
Because we will be…it is said that: “We
are going to send and the sent, the One who

00:25:52.390 --> 00:25:56.010
is sent will not be acceptable to you.

00:25:56.010 --> 00:25:58.020
You will deny, you will defy”.

00:25:58.020 --> 00:26:03.090
Everything is described, even that your hands
will speak at the time of Resurrection, all

00:26:03.090 --> 00:26:04.770
that in that Sura is given.

00:26:04.770 --> 00:26:07.029
It’s very interesting that Sura is.

00:26:07.029 --> 00:26:10.210
So, what I’m saying they are trying to locate
it.

00:26:10.210 --> 00:26:14.510
So many things in different things they are
moving now, also they are trying to make very

00:26:14.510 --> 00:26:22.700
beautiful paintings and drawings and things,
to be able to explain.

00:26:22.700 --> 00:26:24.840
Also they had TV programs.

00:26:24.840 --> 00:26:28.400
So on the TV they told whatever their experience
is, this and that.

00:26:28.400 --> 00:26:33.899
But if you yourself are not capable, you are
not going to influence anyone even if you

00:26:33.899 --> 00:26:35.440
go to the TV or anywhere.

00:26:35.440 --> 00:26:37.990
Nobody’s going to take you seriously.

00:26:37.990 --> 00:26:46.409
So you have to be more serious about it and
to be more earnest to do your meditation.

00:26:46.409 --> 00:26:52.260
Now, there’s another aspect of Sahaja Yoga
that we want people to be married.

00:26:52.260 --> 00:26:57.360
Married but married is not the last thing,
is not the last thing, is just an assistance,

00:26:57.360 --> 00:27:05.840
we can say, a complement from the another
side so that you develop yourself better.

00:27:05.840 --> 00:27:09.950
But any kind of hindrance in the marriage
can be a great hindrance for your ascent.

00:27:09.950 --> 00:27:15.940
So don’t pay any attention to such hindrances,
just get out of it and try to remain your

00:27:15.940 --> 00:27:23.159
Self because only it is your Self which is
going to give you joy and ascent, not anybody

00:27:23.159 --> 00:27:24.159
else.

00:27:24.159 --> 00:27:29.610
It will all work out when if you just keep
to your Self and understand that you are important,

00:27:29.610 --> 00:27:35.919
you have to look after your ascent, also that
the collective of Sahaja Yoga is important.

00:27:35.919 --> 00:27:41.990
It is very important for all of you because
you are so very few and it has to be worked

00:27:41.990 --> 00:27:44.890
out in this country in a big way.

00:27:44.890 --> 00:27:49.779
And everybody was asking why is it that in
New Zealand the people are the same, there’s

00:27:49.779 --> 00:27:52.049
not much changing, why not progressing.

00:27:52.049 --> 00:27:58.130
But I’m sure now more will happen and things
the way have triggered out today it might

00:27:58.130 --> 00:27:59.130
work out.

00:27:59.130 --> 00:28:05.029
So now this is my own submission about it
and if you think that there’s something

00:28:05.029 --> 00:28:09.900
more I should say about it or something you
want to know you can write to Me, I will definitely

00:28:09.900 --> 00:28:10.900
answer such letters.

