You are a Sahaja Yogi, how many women or how
many men have become Sahaja Yogis in this

00:28:36.140 --> 00:28:37.140
world?

00:28:37.140 --> 00:28:40.690
So you are so exceptional.

00:28:40.690 --> 00:28:45.960
And such exceptional people should not bother
about mundane things and useless things.

00:28:45.960 --> 00:28:48.640
They should know their responsibility.

00:28:48.640 --> 00:28:53.690
It is you who will be responsible for the
emancipation of all the New Zealanders.

00:28:53.690 --> 00:28:55.779
And this you must understand.

00:28:55.779 --> 00:28:58.549
You should not try to put your esteem down.

00:28:58.549 --> 00:29:01.210
Try to come up and work it out.

00:29:01.210 --> 00:29:04.910
For every nation is important.

00:29:04.910 --> 00:29:07.649
Some people are extremely alert and some people
are not.

00:29:07.649 --> 00:29:11.059
But now I’m sure it will work out faster.

