trying to…You should show all dignity or

00:29:29.780 --> 00:29:31.070
a hospitality.

00:29:31.070 --> 00:29:32.450
Hospitality helps a lot.

00:29:32.450 --> 00:29:36.240
That’s a very important thing one should
understand.

00:29:36.240 --> 00:29:41.650
Like in India if you come, they’ll see ten
times that you have taken your food, they’ll

00:29:41.650 --> 00:29:45.120
call you, somebody’s not there, where are
you, must come and take.

00:29:45.120 --> 00:29:49.730
