people, see that they are…

00:30:06.200 --> 00:30:12.200
I mean the guests are to be treated in a different
way and the inmates are of a different way

00:30:12.200 --> 00:30:16.179
and that’s what whatever you do your children
are going to learn and behave in the same

00:30:16.179 --> 00:30:17.179
manner.

00:30:17.179 --> 00:30:26.450
So we have to get this culture into us by
which we understand the value of other person,

00:30:26.450 --> 00:30:33.860
of guests who have come, those who are not
yet Sahaja Yogis, who have yet to become Sahaja

00:30:33.860 --> 00:30:36.450
Yogis, who have just got Realization.

00:30:36.450 --> 00:30:44.470
They are to be treated with very great care,
like we can say a seed, which is just sprouted.

00:30:44.470 --> 00:30:46.309
It’s so delicate.

00:30:46.309 --> 00:30:49.309
The plant is in such a delicate way.

00:30:49.309 --> 00:30:54.120
Now you have to replant it properly into Sahaj
field.

00:30:54.120 --> 00:31:01.080
So what do you do is to take out all the sprouted
ones, slowly one by one, keeping proper distance

00:31:01.080 --> 00:31:06.649
between them and try to plant them nicely
into the field of Sahaja Yoga.

00:31:06.649 --> 00:31:12.460
But if you have certain value system, if you
have achieved something, then you shouldn’t

00:31:12.460 --> 00:31:16.960
look down upon them or you should not all
the time make fun of them, because some people

00:31:16.960 --> 00:31:21.039
are sarcastic, some are all the time smiling,
so they think that: “What is wrong with

00:31:21.039 --> 00:31:23.630
us, why are they smiling, all the time?”.

00:31:23.630 --> 00:31:30.279
So there is no need to have artificial smiles,
nor do there’s any need to sort of criticize

00:31:30.279 --> 00:31:37.549
in a way or sometimes [IF] the smile could
be a ridicule, you know people think, they

00:31:37.549 --> 00:31:38.549
misunderstand.

