So we have to built up their confidence, that’s
very important.

00:32:08.260 --> 00:32:13.020
Once you have built up their confidence and
once they start feeling the vibrations and

00:32:13.020 --> 00:32:17.179
everything, they have to trust you, they have
to believe in you.

