So this is the very small outline of the way
I would like New Zealand to come up and to

00:32:26.409 --> 00:32:31.710
act in a sensible way so that people should
say that New Zealanders are the wisest in

00:32:31.710 --> 00:32:32.710
Sahaja Yoga.

